news.title: Singapore, US and Canada dominate foreign investments in Indian real estate market in 2024: Report
news.para: These three countries cumulatively contributed more than 25% of the total equity investments in the country’s real estate in 2024.

news.title: Residential supply grows 12.7% across 13 cities in Q4 2024: Report
news.para: The luxury segment, representing 52% of the total new supply, saw a notable increase from 38% in Q4 2023, marking a 14.4% year-on-year growth in premium properties.

news.title: GRAP III kicks in yet again as AQI deteriorates in NCR
news.para: The capital's AQI rose to 393 in the higher end of the ‘very poor' category on Thursday, as opposed to as opposed to 297 in the poor range a day earlier.

news.title: Pune: Builder from Naigaon lost Rs 8.66 lakh in investment fraud
news.para: He filed a complaint application with the cybercrime police. After preliminary investigations, a case was registered with the Uruli Kanchan police on Wednesday.

news.title: Prateek Group to invest Rs 2,000 crore to build housing project in Ghaziabad
news.para: Prateek Group on Friday announced launch of its new project 'Prateek Grand Begonia', spanning around 15 acre and comprising 2,400 flats.

news.title: NGT slams Odisha state authorities on illegal constructions on Tampara lake
news.para: The NGT's East zone bench in Kolkata expressed strong displeasure over state's lack of response for more than 16 months to notices issued on a petition filed by the Wildlife Society of Orissa (WSO).

news.title: Holcim names chairman Jan Jenisch as CEO and chairman of North American spin-off
news.para: Jenisch, who was CEO at Holcim from 2017 to 2024, has been in charge of steering the 100% separation of the company's North American business into a separate U.S.-listed entity with a potential market valuation of $30 billion.

news.title: RRP Electronics chairman's family buys apartment for Rs 34 crore in Mumbai
news.para: The family has acquired the property spread over 3,132 sq ft on 17th floor of super-premium tower Signia Pearl through Chodankar's wife Priyanka and son Anay Chodankar.

news.title: Liquidation petition filed against Sunac China
news.para: The petition has been filed by a unit of asset manager China Cinda Asset Management, and a hearing is scheduled for March 19, the website shows.

news.title: China's Country Garden proposes deal to reduce offshore debt by $11.6 billion
news.para: The indebted developer has reached an understanding with a lender group made up of seven banks ahead of the company's liquidation hearing on Jan. 20 in Hong Kong, bringing it closer towards a restructuring of its offshore debt.

news.title: New York governor wants to limit hedge funds from buying up homes
news.para: In a statement, Hochul said she would propose legislation this year that would require a 75 day waiting period before large investment firms could place bids on new homes hitting the market and limit certain tax benefits when the firms purchase homes.

news.title: Haveri administration implements digital land records to curb fraud
news.para: The initiative, spanning nine months, seeks to prevent document forgery while ensuring transparent operations. The digitalisation records will be available online, offering improved accessibility and security measures.

news.title: Patiala development body cracks down on two illegal colonies
news.para: PDA officials emphasised their commitment to safeguarding public investments and preventing unregulated development in the district.

news.title: Construction of Bhopal metro phase II to start by month-end
news.para: A consultant for the Madhya Pradesh Metro Rail Corporation Limited (MPMRCL) discussed the plans for phase II of the metro project, stating lessons have been learned from delays in Bhopal metro since 2019.

news.title: Rural development minister inaugurates 50,000 houses under PMAY-G
news.para: The event was held at the Sarusajai Sports Complex. Alongside the launch of the houses, Chouhan also took part in the the distribution of agricultural machinery and equipment to thousands of farmers — a move aimed at enhancing productivity and empowering rural livelihoods.

news.title: Keystone Realtors posts pre-sales of Rs 8.63 billion in Q3 FY25
news.para: Keystone Realtors' collections were at Rs 5.42 billion in the quarter ended December 31, 2024 as compared to Rs 4.52 billion inQ3 FY24, recording a year-on-year growth of 20 per cent.

news.title: Bengaluru: Farmers, developers say e-khatas stalling their property sales
news.para: But there are a lot of hiccups in getting e-khatas in non-BBMP areas and all kinds of objections are being raised to deny the document to us," said developer HM Jagadish Gowda.

news.title: Noida: Farmer stops Unitech from constructing road for Express City project
news.para: Construction at the project, which has been delayed by nearly a decade over financial and operational troubles within the company, had resumed in Sept last year after the Supreme Court replaced the company's management with a board of directors in 2020.

news.title: Godrej Properties acquires 24-acre land parcel in Indore
news.para: Gaurav Pandey, MD & CEO, Godrej Properties said, "With residential plotted developments gaining momentum, the Indore bypass road presents a promising opportunity for us to expand."

news.title: Greater Noida: Director of Himalaya Infra arrested in connection with Hathras land scam
news.para: The scam is linked to the alleged irregularities in the acquisition of about 42 hectares of land by the Yamuna Expressway Industrial Development Authority (YEIDA) in 2011-12.
